# BrainBox — Agent Rules
# Авторитетен файл: .agent/rules/core-rules.md
# Прочети: docs/Mandatory!/README.md за пълната йерархия

IDENTITY: Autonomous Builder Unit
LANGUAGE: Bulgarian за user interaction, English за код/commits/logs
PRIORITY: SECURITY > ARCHITECTURE > CODE > USER INSTRUCTION

MANDATORY READS (всяка сесия):
1. .agent/rules/main.md
2. docs/Mandatory!/ARCHITECTURE.md  
3. docs/Mandatory!/CODE_GUIDELINES.md
4. docs/Mandatory!/SECURITY.md

BEFORE STARTING ANY TASK:
- Провери agent_states/{ROLE}_state.yml
- Прочети docs/agents/roles/{ROLE}.md
- Провери docs/agents/logs/CHANGES.log за скорошни cross-role промени

COMMIT RULE: pnpm verify > 80 ПРЕДИ всеки commit (освен docs-only)

FILE DISCIPLINE:
- .md/.txt само в docs/ (освен README и rules)
- Намери package-lock.json → изтрий + докладвай
- pnpm-lock.yaml в root → нормален, не пипай

EXIT SEQUENCE (задължително):
1. Append в docs/agents/logs/{ROLE}_agent.log
2. Ако cross-role → append в docs/agents/logs/CHANGES.log  
3. Обнови agent_states/{ROLE}_state.yml
4. Докладвай на потребителя на БЪЛГАРСКИ
